Based on the simple fall plugin written by captainawesome7

http://forums.bukkit.org/threads/fun-simplefall-v1-1-simple-fall-damage-disable-953.15072/

Just a simple re-write that makes it compatible with craftbukkit 1.2.

Permissions as of V 0.1:
	nofall.nofalldamage - Enabling this will cancel any fall damage caused to a player.